    public class MaterialDnd
extends gwt.material.design.client.base.MaterialWidget
implements HasDraggable
    Drag and drop feature on Material Design specs are great UX guide to provide a delightful motion on dragging and dropping gestures.

    Java Usage

    MaterialDnd dnd = new MaterialDnd();
 // Set the draggable object
 dnd.setDraggable(widget);

 // Set the ignored widget when dragging the element
 dnd.setIgnoreFrom(toolbar);
    Author:
    kevzlou7979
    See Also:
    Drag and Drop
